<content type="str">A server at a Kentucky Buffalo Wild Wings restaurant was shocked to see what a customer left in place of a tip. 
 
According to LGBTQ Nation, Kyle Griffith was working at a Louisville Buffalo Wild Wings, when he got a surprising note in place of a tip. The server says prior to the incident, it was just a normal night like any other. 
